%h1 About us
%p PragAuthor is a web site for consolidating sales figures that Authors receive from different sources.<br />At this moment we support Amazon, Barnes & Noble and SmashWords.
%p Pavel Gabriel and Yves Hanoulle are founders of this service.
%p We love hearing from interested authors, bloggers and press!<br />Please email any questions to <a href="mailto:welcome@pragauthor.com">welcome@pragauthor.com</a>

